rows.label: fev06_140_107_msg0001
rows.name: Right...let's head for Goth Isut Port!

rows.label: fev06_140_107_msg0002
rows.name: Can we make it a leisurely walk?

rows.label: fev06_140_107_msg0004
rows.name:
It's been yonks since I last went
home to Luxuria.

rows.label: fev06_140_107_msg0005
rows.name:
I've been thinking of Acedia as my home
so long now, it feels weird to leave.
I want to enjoy my last moments here.

rows.label: fev06_140_107_msg0006
rows.name:
You can be shockingly sentimental
sometimes.

rows.label: fev06_140_107_msg0009
rows.name:
Gonna take some Acedian presents for
the folk you haven't seen in a while?

rows.label: fev06_140_107_msg0010
rows.name:
Hah! As if my old man would
want any of that.

rows.label: fev06_140_107_msg0011
rows.name:
C'mon, let's start walking.
To Goth Isut Port!

rows.label: fev06_140_107_msg0012
rows.name:
You could grab a swig of Odifa
along the way!

rows.label: fev06_140_107_msg0013
rows.name:
They don't have that stuff in Luxuria,
so this could be your last chance!
